cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.SY 

The paper deals with interference management in wireless networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), machine learning (cs.LG), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, the focus on user admission control and optimization techniques suggests that cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.SI, cs.LG, and cs.SY.
